# BillSG — Tech Steering

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: Next.js 16 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
- Bill Parsing: AWS Textract
- LLM: Amazon Bedrock (Claude)
- File Storage: AWS S3
- MCP Server: Custom Node.js server exposing Singapore 2026 healthcare policy data
- Rules Engine: Pure TypeScript — deterministic eligibility logic, no AI
- Scraper: Node.js + Cheerio — scrapes live MOH/CPF/AIC pages to keep MCP server current
- Hosting: Vercel (frontend) + AWS Lambda (API routes)

