## Coding Standards
- All files in TypeScript — no plain JavaScript
- All API routes use Next.js App Router format
- All functions must have explicit type annotations
- No console.log in production code — use proper error handling
- Every API route must validate inputs before processing

## Environment Variables Required
- AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID
- AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY
- AWS_REGION
- BEDROCK_MODEL_ID
- S3_BUCKET_NAME
- MCP_SERVER_URL
- SCRAPER_SCHEDULE

## Key Constraints
- Never store sensitive patient data beyond the current session
- Never log bill contents or personal health information
- Always show disclaimer on every AI-generated output
- Bill parsing targets Singapore public hospital bill format only (SGH, TTSH, NUH, SKH, NTFGH, CGH)